data.details: This workshop will prepare you to join, if you choose, a new Council-Wide Team of Enrichment Specialists dedicated to developing and sharing exceptional Girl Scout program. Training will include: - Tips for planning a workshop for groups of all sizes - Preparing/organizing materials - Presentation delivery techniques relating to each area of interest - Resources galore! For more information contact: Mary Rose Smith at maryrosesmithgs@gmail.com or Gail Rankin at gail.rankin1@gmail.com.
